he Southern states with prospects of thunderstorms later in the day. It forecast day and night temperatures of the region to be 32 to 34 degree Celsius and 20 to 24 degree Celsius respectively. Vanguard News Nigeria. The Nigerian Meteorological Agency ( NiMet) has predicted sunny, hazy and chances of thundery activities over the coastal cities for Sunday. November 30, 2019 In "News" The Nigerian Meteorological Agency (NiMet) has predicted partly cloudy conditions over the central states of the country on Monday with thundery showers over Jalingo and Ibi in the afternoon and evening. April 16, 2017 In "News" The Nigerian Meteorological Agency (NiMet) has predicted sunny and hazy conditions over the country for Thursday with chances of thunderstorms over coastal cities. NiMet’s Weather outlook on Wednesday in Abuja predicted sunny and hazy conditions over Northern states throughout forecast period with day and night temperatures of 34 to 36… December 5, 2019 In "News"